00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:45.000
I missed you so much.

00:04:45.920 --> 00:04:47.639
Nanny missed you too.

00:04:52.480 --> 00:04:53.079
It smells so good.

00:04:55.600 --> 00:04:57.519
