00:04:57.519 --> 00:04:59.519
Just laundry and cooking...

00:05:00.839 --> 00:05:02.839
...the smell of smoke and soap.

00:05:03.519 --> 00:05:04.800
It's the smell of home.

00:05:08.519 --> 00:05:09.360
It's so good to be home.

00:05:12.199 --> 00:05:13.519
My good Yingying.

00:05:14.360 --> 00:05:16.240
