Granny, come back for congee.

00:19:09.920 --> 00:19:10.799
Remember,

00:19:11.160 --> 00:19:12.519
don't deal with Japs.

00:19:12.519 --> 00:19:13.440
The congee is getting cold.

00:19:13.680 --> 00:19:14.680
Remember.

00:19:58.880 --> 00:19:59.640
Nanny.

00:20:03.480 --> 00:20:04.119
Yingying.

00:20:04.559 --> 00:20:06.480
Where did you run off to so early?

00:20:06.920 --> 00:20:07.759
It's been too long since I was back.

00:20:08.000 --> 00:20:09.079
Just strolling around the village.

00:20:09.960 --> 00:20:11.039
Are you hungry?

00:20:11.680 --> 00:20:13.240
I'll go make breakfast for the master.

00:20:13.240 --> 00:20:14.160
Nanny, wait.

00:20:14.160 --> 00:20:14.759
What is it?

00:20:14.759 --> 00:20:15.240
Sit down.

00:20:15.960 --> 00:20:16.559
I have something to ask you.

00:20:17.440 --> 00:20:18.200
What is it?

00:20:19.319 --> 00:20:20.079
Recently,

00:20:20.920 --> 00:20:22.240
has someone come here?

00:20:22.519 --> 00:20:23.319
Come here?

00:20:25.960 --> 00:20:26.799
Who came?

00:20:27.400 --> 00:20:28.400
I'm asking you.

00:20:29.440 --> 00:20:30.599
How would I know?

00:20:31.279 --> 00:20:31.759
Really, no one.

00:20:32.559 --> 00:20:33.559
Really, no one.

00:20:34.440 --> 00:20:36.079
Then what is this?

00:20:39.319 --> 00:20:39.680
This...

00:20:40.319 --> 00:20:41.839
...is a needle.

00:20:44.480 --> 00:20:45.279
Haven't seen it.

00:20:46.160 --> 00:20:47.079
Haven't seen it.

00:20:48.160 --> 00:20:48.559
Alright.

00:20:48.559 --> 00:20:49.319
Then it's nothing.

00:20:49.839 --> 00:20:50.440
Ying'er.

00:20:52.559 --> 00:20:53.200
Brother.

00:20:53.799 --> 00:20:54.440
You're here.

00:20:54.880 --> 00:20:56.160
Dad sent me to bring you both back.

00:20:56.920 --> 00:20:58.519
I'll go make breakfast for the master.

00:21:01.000 --> 00:21:01.640
Then let's go.

00:21:02.279 --> 00:21:02.759
Ying'er.

00:21:05.200 --> 00:21:07.240
That colonel who came with you,

00:21:07.799 --> 00:21:09.079
are you sure he's a Japanese officer?

00:21:09.559 --> 00:21:10.759
You called him 'colonel'.

00:21:10.759 --> 00:21:12.000
What else would he be if not a Japanese officer?

00:21:14.720 --> 00:21:15.480
What's wrong?

00:21:16.759 --> 00:21:17.759
Nothing, nothing, nothing.

00:21:18.240 --> 00:21:18.839
Really, nothing's wrong.

00:21:19.079 --> 00:21:19.640
Nothing.

00:21:25.240 --> 00:21:25.519
Brother.

00:21:26.400 --> 00:21:26.799
Brother.

00:21:28.240 --> 00:21:29.839
Brother, why are you walking so fast?

00:21:30.160 --> 00:21:30.519
Hey.

00:21:31.759 --> 00:21:32.920
I'm calling you.

00:21:33.240 --> 00:21:34.079
What's wrong with you?

00:21:36.000 --> 00:21:36.519
Nothing's wrong.

00:21:36.519 --> 00:21:37.160
I'm fine.

00:21:38.039 --> 00:21:38.599
Nothing.

00:21:39.200 --> 00:21:40.079
Really, nothing.

00:21:40.680 --> 00:21:42.039
Saying 'nothing' means something *is* wrong.

00:21:43.359 --> 00:21:44.000
Let's go.

00:21:44.000 --> 00:21:44.759
Dad is waiting.

00:21:46.680 --> 00:21:49.039
Dad isn't angry with me anymore?

00:21:49.359 --> 00:21:50.240
Why did he call me back?

00:21:51.279 --> 00:21:52.039
I don't know either.

00:21:52.559 --> 00:21:53.160
Don't ask.

00:21:53.160 --> 00:21:54.200
You'll know when we get there.

00:21:55.920 --> 00:21:56.279
Hey.

00:21:58.279 --> 00:21:59.039
Listen to me.

00:22:00.400 --> 00:22:01.880
No matter what happens at home,

00:22:02.359 --> 00:22:03.680
you must let me know immediately.

00:22:04.559 --> 00:22:05.519
Don't hide anything from me.

00:22:07.960 --> 00:22:08.640
What are you talking about?

00:22:08.640 --> 00:22:09.680
What hiding?

00:22:09.880 --> 00:22:10.960
What could possibly be hidden from you?

00:22:11.240 --> 00:22:12.119
Did you hear me?

00:22:12.440 --> 00:22:13.039
Alright, alright, alright.

00:22:13.319 --> 00:22:13.720
Let's go.

00:22:17.160 --> 00:22:17.960
Yingying.

00:22:18.400 --> 00:22:19.200
Let's go.

00:22:19.200 --> 00:22:20.799
The master is waiting for you.

00:22:23.119 --> 00:22:24.200
How strange.

00:22:35.319 --> 00:22:37.200
Biying, stop making noise.

00:22:37.200 --> 00:22:38.880
I'll go prepare some food.

00:22:41.039 --> 00:22:42.759
Put in a good word for me, brother.

00:22:43.240 --> 00:22:44.559
Dad, we're back.

00:22:46.880 --> 00:22:47.599
Dad.

00:22:49.480 --> 00:22:50.160
Follow me.

00:23:25.160 --> 00:23:26.039
Is this the place?

00:23:26.039 --> 00:23:26.920
This is it.

00:23:30.480 --> 00:23:32.079
Where is the hidden sentry's bunk?

00:23:33.440 --> 00:23:34.160
Here.

00:23:35.599 --> 00:23:36.319
Is this it?

00:23:36.759 --> 00:23:37.240
Yes.

00:23:39.480 --> 00:23:41.440
Last night when this sentry was changing shifts,

00:23:41.839 --> 00:23:42.960
he wasn't at his post.

00:23:43.720 --> 00:23:44.759
We thought he came back early,

00:23:44.759 --> 00:23:45.599
so we didn't pay it any mind.

00:23:46.000 --> 00:23:47.759
We only discovered he was missing this morning.

00:24:07.319 --> 00:24:08.200
Is this the man?

00:24:09.079 --> 00:24:09.680
Yes.

00:24:11.000 --> 00:24:12.920
What time did he start his shift?

00:24:13.960 --> 00:24:15.440
He changed shifts at nine-thirty last night.

00:24:15.720 --> 00:24:16.759
The guard change was at eleven-thirty.

00:24:17.039 --> 00:24:19.119
Did anyone notice anything unusual?

00:24:20.640 --> 00:24:21.079
No.

00:24:25.559 --> 00:24:26.680
Send men to find him immediately.

00:24:26.680 --> 00:24:27.920
The list of personnel

00:24:27.920 --> 00:24:29.160
who returned to the barracks after nine-thirty last night.

00:24:29.680 --> 00:24:30.079
Yes, sir.

00:24:31.839 --> 00:24:32.960
Where is the sentry post?

00:24:32.960 --> 00:24:34.079
Take me to see it.

00:24:34.960 --> 00:24:35.640
This way.

00:24:41.119 --> 00:24:41.599
Captain.

00:24:42.400 --> 00:24:44.480
From the position of that guard post up there,

00:24:44.519 --> 00:24:47.759
down to this position here,

00:24:47.759 --> 00:24:49.160
extending all the way over there.

00:24:49.160 --> 00:24:50.359
All of this area

00:24:50.359 --> 00:24:52.680
is within our hidden sentry perimeter.

00:25:01.200 --> 00:25:01.559
Captain.

00:25:03.400 --> 00:25:04.000
This is

00:25:04.000 --> 00:25:05.680
the list of personnel who returned

00:25:05.680 --> 00:25:07.200
to the barracks after nine-thirty last night.

00:25:08.759 --> 00:25:09.759
Any suspicious individuals?

00:25:14.079 --> 00:25:14.480
This one.

00:25:15.599 --> 00:25:16.559
This is a colonel

00:25:16.559 --> 00:25:17.359
assigned by headquarters yesterday

00:25:17.359 --> 00:25:18.319
to be billeted in the barracks.

00:25:18.319 --> 00:25:20.160
He also returned after nine-thirty.

00:25:21.359 --> 00:25:22.039
A colonel?

00:25:25.720 --> 00:25:28.279
Could it be that newly arrived colonel?

00:25:28.480 --> 00:25:29.160
That's correct.

00:25:33.440 --> 00:25:34.880
I know he left the police brigade

00:25:34.880 --> 00:25:37.400
after nine-thirty.

00:25:41.480 --> 00:25:42.960
Listen up, all of you.

00:25:44.680 --> 00:25:47.559
Conduct a precise search.

00:25:47.559 --> 00:25:49.119
Search inch by inch.

00:25:49.119 --> 00:25:50.799
You must locate the primary crime scene.

00:25:50.799 --> 00:25:52.319
Yes, sir!

00:26:36.160 --> 00:26:36.880
Xia'er.

00:26:37.599 --> 00:26:38.279
Ying'er.

00:26:40.119 --> 00:26:41.200
Both of you, kneel down.

00:26:48.200 --> 00:26:50.599
Kowtow three times to the villagers.

00:27:11.039 --> 00:27:12.240
Father...

00:27:12.720 --> 00:27:13.839
Who...

00:27:15.079 --> 00:27:16.519
are all these people?

00:27:18.200 --> 00:27:19.559
In the twenty-seventh year of the Republic,

00:27:21.559 --> 00:27:23.160
on the twelfth day of the third lunar month.

00:27:25.839 --> 00:27:26.720
That day,

00:27:27.799 --> 00:27:28.680
the weather was fine.

00:27:31.359 --> 00:27:32.799
At seven in the morning.

00:27:36.920 --> 00:27:37.920
Villagers!

00:27:38.319 --> 00:27:39.519
Listen to me!

00:27:40.160 --> 00:27:40.920
Today,

00:27:41.319 --> 00:27:43.119
we will be issuing Good Citizen Certificates.

00:27:43.559 --> 00:27:44.519
Everyone

00:27:44.960 --> 00:27:46.200
must assemble here.

00:27:47.240 --> 00:27:47.839
From now on,

00:27:48.279 --> 00:27:49.359
anyone without a Good Citizen Certificate

00:27:49.880 --> 00:27:51.359
will be sent directly to prison.

00:27:53.359 --> 00:27:53.680
Good.

00:27:54.160 --> 00:27:54.799
Now,

00:27:55.359 --> 00:27:56.319
form two lines.

00:27:56.599 --> 00:27:57.759
All of you, form two lines!

00:30:15.079 --> 00:30:20.160
People at birth are naturally good.

00:30:20.559 --> 00:30:26.039
Their natures are similar, their habits become different.

00:30:26.039 --> 00:30:31.640
If negligently taught, their nature will deteriorate.

00:30:31.640 --> 00:30:37.480
The way of teaching lies in concentration.

00:30:37.480 --> 00:30:43.480
Long ago, Mencius's mother chose a neighborhood.

00:30:43.480 --> 00:30:49.759
Her son wouldn't learn, she cut the loom's thread.

00:30:49.759 --> 00:30:55.799
Dou of Yan Mountain had the right method.

00:30:55.799 --> 00:31:01.640
He taught five sons, each achieved fame.

00:31:01.640 --> 00:31:07.319
To raise without teaching is the father's fault.

00:31:07.319 --> 00:31:13.200
To teach without severity is the teacher's laziness.

00:32:19.440 --> 00:32:21.440
Among the thirty-six villages on the island,

00:32:21.440 --> 00:32:23.279
more than twelve thousand eight hundred people

00:32:24.599 --> 00:32:26.400
were killed or fled.

00:32:28.319 --> 00:32:30.000
In the end, only Tanjia Bay

00:32:30.640 --> 00:32:32.160
and Shangbiao, two villages,

00:32:33.680 --> 00:32:34.880
with over eighteen hundred people, remained.

00:32:38.279 --> 00:32:40.079
What you are kneeling before now

00:32:40.279 --> 00:32:41.599
is a mass grave of ten thousand.

00:32:44.160 --> 00:32:45.839
Furthermore, at the west entrance of Yunong Village,

00:32:47.039 --> 00:32:48.359
there is another mass grave of a thousand.

00:32:51.400 --> 00:32:52.720
In every village,

00:32:53.559 --> 00:32:54.680
there are graves of a hundred.

00:32:57.400 --> 00:32:58.799
Why is this?

00:33:01.519 --> 00:33:02.279
For no reason.

00:33:06.359 --> 00:33:07.799
Your father has been to many places.

00:33:09.079 --> 00:33:10.920
Japanese militarists

00:33:11.319 --> 00:33:12.240
are the most

00:33:13.839 --> 00:33:15.240
inhumane soldiers I have ever seen.

00:33:17.000 --> 00:33:18.720
They are simply a pack of beasts.

00:33:22.319 --> 00:33:24.359
In the early spring of the Republic's twenty-seventh year,

00:33:24.640 --> 00:33:26.000
you left Guangzhou heading north.

00:33:27.759 --> 00:33:28.880
That very year,

00:33:28.880 --> 00:33:30.599
the Japanese occupied Sanzao Island.

00:33:33.039 --> 00:33:33.680
Therefore,

00:33:34.880 --> 00:33:37.119
the family completely lost contact with you.

00:33:38.599 --> 00:33:41.160
You know nothing

00:33:42.119 --> 00:33:42.960
of all that happened here.

00:33:45.640 --> 00:33:46.519
During those years,

00:33:48.279 --> 00:33:49.839
all the residents of the island

00:33:50.960 --> 00:33:52.000
endured a massacre

00:33:53.079 --> 00:33:54.960
that defied human justice

00:33:56.039 --> 00:33:57.599
and conscience.

00:34:05.640 --> 00:34:06.319
I brought you here

00:34:06.319 --> 00:34:07.279
because I want to tell you:

00:34:09.880 --> 00:34:11.239
All the villagers on the island

00:34:12.760 --> 00:34:14.559
regard the Japanese as mortal enemies.

00:34:18.480 --> 00:34:21.400
You cannot be with that Japanese soldier.

00:34:21.400 --> 00:34:23.320
I could never accept this.

00:34:26.679 --> 00:34:28.480
If you are with that Japanese officer,

00:34:29.280 --> 00:34:30.639
the surviving villagers on the island

00:34:31.920 --> 00:34:33.519
will not accept you either.

00:34:53.000 --> 00:34:53.800
Ying'er.

00:34:55.320 --> 00:34:56.159
Weren't you asking me

00:34:56.159 --> 00:34:58.000
how Ke Wen became the way he is now?

00:35:00.280 --> 00:35:03.719
He crawled out from a pile of corpses.

00:35:49.239 --> 00:35:50.360
I should go home.

00:36:01.800 --> 00:36:02.719
When he discovered

00:36:02.920 --> 00:36:03.840
that the entire Caotang Village

00:36:03.840 --> 00:36:05.440
was left with only him,

00:36:06.840 --> 00:36:07.920
the person he used to be

00:36:08.400 --> 00:36:09.920
could no longer bear to live on.

00:36:13.119 --> 00:36:13.599
Ying'er.

00:36:14.360 --> 00:36:14.920
Listen to your father.

00:36:15.960 --> 00:36:17.840
Stop associating with that Japanese officer.

00:36:53.159 --> 00:36:55.599
A living person just vanished like that.

00:36:55.880 --> 00:36:58.519
It's simply unbelievable.

00:36:58.519 --> 00:37:01.280
I'll go find a place to sit down first.

00:37:21.679 --> 00:37:22.119
Your Excellency

00:37:23.119 --> 00:37:23.719
Call me Colonel.

00:37:23.719 --> 00:37:24.519
Colonel, Your Excellency.

00:37:24.679 --> 00:37:26.199
I was very rude yesterday.

00:37:29.119 --> 00:37:29.760
Please enjoy your meal.

00:37:29.920 --> 00:37:31.079
Sasaki.

00:37:31.760 --> 00:37:33.000
Sit down and have a meal with me.

00:37:33.480 --> 00:37:33.840
Sit.

00:37:36.199 --> 00:37:37.519
Sit down and have a meal with me.

00:37:37.760 --> 00:37:39.480
I'm greatly honored.

00:37:47.840 --> 00:37:48.199
Thank you.

00:37:52.199 --> 00:37:53.199
Captain Inoue.

00:37:53.199 --> 00:37:55.079
Did you sleep in the brig last night?

00:37:55.079 --> 00:37:57.239
Of course. The Colonel's two-day order isn't up yet.

00:37:57.400 --> 00:37:58.519
I dare not leave without permission.

00:38:02.360 --> 00:38:05.639
The officers' mess food is quite good.

00:38:05.639 --> 00:38:07.639
Yes, yes.

00:38:14.480 --> 00:38:17.880
The navy's breakfast is always better than the army's.

00:38:17.880 --> 00:38:21.719
And the pilots' breakfast is always better than the officers'.

00:38:21.719 --> 00:38:22.880
An extra egg.

00:38:22.880 --> 00:38:24.039
And a piece of chocolate.

00:38:24.840 --> 00:38:25.599
You know,

00:38:25.599 --> 00:38:26.599
there are many girls in Tokyo

00:38:26.599 --> 00:38:28.079
who are willing to marry a pilot

00:38:28.079 --> 00:38:29.760
just to get that piece of chocolate.

00:38:29.760 --> 00:38:34.760
The chocolate is sweet, but being a young widow is hard, isn't it?

00:38:40.719 --> 00:38:41.320
Thank you.

00:38:57.599 --> 00:38:58.320
You all eat.

00:39:02.920 --> 00:39:03.760
This is yours, Colonel.

00:39:03.760 --> 00:39:04.280
Please, eat.

00:39:07.599 --> 00:39:08.800
Thank you.

00:39:16.119 --> 00:39:17.599
Go ahead and eat it.

00:39:18.679 --> 00:39:19.880
Thank you.

00:39:27.840 --> 00:39:29.679
What brings you here for breakfast?

00:39:29.679 --> 00:39:31.239
Doesn't the police battalion have a mess hall?

00:39:33.000 --> 00:39:33.760
Last night,

00:39:33.760 --> 00:39:35.199
a sentry from the garrison went missing.

00:39:35.960 --> 00:39:36.559
An incident like this

00:39:36.559 --> 00:39:37.760
hasn't happened for over a year.

00:39:38.440 --> 00:39:39.360
We investigated

00:39:39.360 --> 00:39:40.440
the list of all personnel

00:39:40.440 --> 00:39:42.639
who returned to the barracks after 9:30 yesterday.

00:39:47.440 --> 00:39:48.880
That list should include me as well.

00:39:49.360 --> 00:39:51.400
So you're here to investigate me?

00:39:51.760 --> 00:39:53.360
This has nothing to do with you.

00:40:01.440 --> 00:40:03.280
Based on the preliminary investigation,

00:40:04.280 --> 00:40:08.000
the missing sentry

00:40:08.000 --> 00:40:11.360
is heavily linked to the Chinese.

00:40:13.599 --> 00:40:14.760
How could such a thing happen?

00:40:14.840 --> 00:40:15.800
Does it happen often?

00:40:16.079 --> 00:40:17.440
Since we landed on the island in Showa 13,

00:40:17.440 --> 00:40:19.639
nearly forty officers and soldiers

00:40:19.639 --> 00:40:21.440
have gone missing or been killed.

00:40:21.880 --> 00:40:23.079
The worst incident

00:40:23.079 --> 00:40:24.519
was when they killed twelve of our men.

00:40:25.320 --> 00:40:28.639
It's truly a detestable place.

00:40:29.599 --> 00:40:30.599
Why is it like this?

00:40:33.280 --> 00:40:35.320
Sanzao Island is not far from Macau, China.

00:40:35.840 --> 00:40:37.679
That place can hide anything.

00:40:38.280 --> 00:40:38.760
Macau, China.

00:40:40.159 --> 00:40:40.679
Yes.

00:40:41.039 --> 00:40:43.360
Macau, China is Portuguese territory.

00:40:43.599 --> 00:40:44.840
It's a neutral zone.

00:40:44.920 --> 00:40:45.719
The night before last,

00:40:45.880 --> 00:40:49.440
the gunboat that attacked our transport ship, the *Amemaru*,

00:40:49.760 --> 00:40:53.079
was a Chiang regime vessel hiding there.

00:40:53.239 --> 00:40:54.760
There are also gangs and assassins there

00:40:55.039 --> 00:40:56.880
who often come to the island to cause trouble.

00:41:00.440 --> 00:41:01.239
That should be easy then.

00:41:01.239 --> 00:41:02.400
Such a small place.

00:41:02.400 --> 00:41:03.880
Just send troops to occupy it. Darn it.

00:41:06.639 --> 00:41:07.599
No.

00:41:08.039 --> 00:41:10.000
We can occupy China, the Philippines, Burma,

00:41:10.000 --> 00:41:13.679
Singapore, and Hong Kong, China.

00:41:13.960 --> 00:41:14.719
But we cannot occupy

00:41:14.719 --> 00:41:15.639
Portuguese-affiliated Macau, China.

00:41:16.639 --> 00:41:17.119
Why?

00:41:18.519 --> 00:41:19.239
It's said that Brazil sent a diplomatic note

00:41:19.239 --> 00:41:20.239
to our Foreign Ministry.

00:41:20.239 --> 00:41:21.119
The note stated

00:41:21.119 --> 00:41:22.920
that if we militarily occupy Macau, China,

00:41:22.920 --> 00:41:24.039
Brazil would expel all of our

00:41:24.039 --> 00:41:25.880
Japanese nationals there—over three million people—

00:41:25.960 --> 00:41:28.079
and send them back to the Japanese mainland.

00:41:28.679 --> 00:41:29.840
The military headquarters fears

00:41:30.000 --> 00:41:32.440
that repatriating these three million Japanese

00:41:32.800 --> 00:41:35.159
would cause domestic chaos beyond control.

00:41:35.880 --> 00:41:36.119
Therefore,

00:41:36.119 --> 00:41:37.239
they strictly forbid us from provoking that place.

00:41:37.239 --> 00:41:38.679
That's how it is.

00:41:39.440 --> 00:41:40.559
I didn't expect a mere company commander like you

00:41:40.880 --> 00:41:41.840
to know so much.

00:41:43.599 --> 00:41:45.239
This is all from our battalion commander.

00:41:46.039 --> 00:41:46.800
Captain Inoue?

